{"tid":347319,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"熱狗去蘋果貼 LINK 宣傳熱時","createTime":"2017-08-04T17:09:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T06:42:51.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a4b963484f28cdfa114c5a3205a6d936982053a6","tid":347319,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:09:45.000Z","msg":"熱狗去蘋果貼 LINK 宣傳熱時 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s2.postimg.org/d8wff3m61/LINK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs2.postimg.org%2Fd8wff3m61%2FLINK.jpg&h=4a775016&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事源：毒果報左呢單野！<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170805/57042535\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170805%2F57042535&d=WXy6%2FEefggLTTy5in0AyrlzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=755adcf1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170805%2F57042535&h=840b7b80\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170805/57042535</a><br />\n<br />\n浸大學者為哲學書寫序言批香港政治腐敗   遭商務印政治審查抽起<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170804/large/1501857425_b003.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170804%2Flarge%2F1501857425_b003.png&h=2a232186&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不要以為政治審查是內地獨有，其實審查歪風早已入侵香港。中資背景「三中商」之一的商務印書館被浸大人文及創作系副教授黃國鉅投訴作出政治審查，要求他刪除為一本哲學書籍寫序言時，批評本港近10年政治敗壞的段落，「我堅決一字不改，結果序言被抽起，現在書店看到的版本，已經不見了我的序言。」<br />\n<br />\n黃國鉅周五晚上在facebook發文，指近日獲網媒《香港01》旗下的「01哲學」專頁邀請，為專頁結集的一本名為《無睡意哲學》的哲學書籍寫序言。他在序言提及「不知道什麼原因，香港近年吹起哲學風......究竟這現象原因何在？如何解釋？我自己比較相信尼采的說法：一個文化興盛的時候，不需要哲學，哲學流行，可能是文化出現危機或衰敗的徵兆。香港近十年政治敗壞、社會紛亂，荒謬不義之事無日無之，尤其雨傘革命後，年青人感覺到沮喪迷茫，希望在哲學中尋找出路，也是正常之事。」"},{"pid":"9cb31be845a79a6e3a417459834fac2a95f1551f","tid":347319,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T06:42:51.000Z","msg":"去共媒貼共黨link有乜問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}